Initialization Parameters

Initialization parameters perform the following functions:

  • Set limits for the entire database
  • Set user or process limits
  • Set limits on database resources
  • Affect performance

Shortcuts to Parameter Names

If you know the name of the parameter you want, select its abbreviation. Otherwise, scroll down to see the entire list.
